OL,3,CHouseholds set for lower energy bills
OL,4,Camid price cap shake-up
OL,6,FHouseholds are set to learn their
OL,7,Fenergy bills will fall by around 7%
OL,8,Ffrom April in a shake-up of costs
OL,9,Fafter the Government promised they
OL,10,Fwill receive an average #150 cut.
OL,12,FLatest predictions suggest Ofgem will
OL,13,Freduce the energy price cap by #117 to
OL,14,F#1,641 a year for a typical dual fuel
OL,15,Fhousehold from April 1 when it makes
OL,16,Fits announcement on Wednesday.
