OL,3,CHouseholds set for lower energy bills
OL,4,Camid price cap shake-up
OL,6,FChancellor Rachel Reeves said in
OL,7,FNovember that #150 would be cut from
OL,8,Fthe average household bill from April
OL,9,Fby scrapping the Energy Company
OL,10,FObligation (Eco) scheme introduced by
OL,11,Fthe Tories in government.
OL,13,FCustomers have been warned not to
OL,14,Fexpect a straight #150 discount on
OL,15,Ftheir bills, and that the cut will
OL,16,Fdepend on the size and type of
OL,17,Fhousehold and how much energy it uses.
