OL,3,CHouseholds set for lower energy bills
OL,4,Camid price cap shake-up
OL,6,F"While the saving will be #150 for the
OL,7,Faverage household, it is important to
OL,8,Fnote that the discount is applied to
OL,9,Fthe unit rate. Therefore, households
OL,10,Fwill experience significantly
OL,11,Fdifferent savings depending on their
OL,12,Fenergy consumption, some much higher
OL,13,Fand others substantially lower than
OL,14,F#150.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
