OL,3,CHouseholds set for lower energy bills
OL,4,Camid price cap shake-up
OL,6,F"The bulk of this change is expected
OL,7,Fto be applied to your electricity
OL,8,Fprice per unit, so your exact savings
OL,9,Fwill depend on your usage; look out
OL,10,Ffor communications from your energy
OL,11,Fprovider in the coming weeks to see
OL,12,Fhow it will affect your bills."
OL,14,FSimon Francis, co-ordinator of the End
OL,15,FFuel Poverty Coalition, urged
OL,16,Fhouseholds to note the changes in unit
OL,17,Fcosts and standing charges, rather
OL,18,Fthan focus on the headline "average
OL,19,Fenergy bill".
