OL,3,CHouseholds set for lower energy bills
OL,4,Camid price cap shake-up
OL,6,FHe said: "We know that energy bills
OL,7,Fcan be confusing and trying to decide
OL,8,Fwhen to switch tariffs or change
OL,9,Fsupplier is a big decision which can
OL,10,Foverwhelm people.
OL,12,F"As well as setting the price cap,
OL,13,FOfgem should play a greater role in
OL,14,Fensuring that the tariffs reaching the
OL,15,Fmarket are fair and don't discriminate
OL,16,Fagainst specific customer groups.
OL,18,F"Sadly the responsibility currently
OL,19,Ffalls to households to pay careful
OL,20,Fattention to any changes in their unit
OL,21,Fcosts and standing charges."
